msgstr ""
"Metal3DataTemplate 定义要传递给 BareMetalHost 的附加 metaData（请注意，Edge "
"解决方案目前不支持 networkData）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:151
msgid ""
"Note for simplicity this example assumes a single-node controlplane, where "
"the BareMetalHost is configured with an IP of <literal>192.168.125.200</"
