#: l10n/source/edge.xml:281
msgid ""
"For each of the systems that you want to control with Elemental, add the "
"installation media and boot the device. After installation, it will reboot "
"and register itself."
msgstr ""
"对于您要使用 Elemental 控制的每个系统，请添加安装媒体并引导设备。安装后，系统"
"会重引导并自行注册。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:282
msgid ""
