"机清单）中。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:283
msgid ""
"Do not remove the installation medium until you’ve seen the login prompt; "
"during first-boot files are still accessed on the USB stick."
msgstr ""
"在出现登录提示之前，请勿移除安装媒体；在首次引导期间，仍需访问 USB 记忆棒上的"
