msgstr ""
"Edge Image Builder 使用<emphasis>定义文件</emphasis>来修改 SLE Micro 映像。这"
"些文件包含大部分可配置选项。其中的许多选项将在不同的组件部分中重复出现，因此"
"下面列出并解释了这些选项。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><tip><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1050
msgid ""
"Full list of customization options in the definition file can be found in "
"the <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/edge-image-builder/blob/"
"release-1.0/docs/building-images.md#image-definition-file\">upstream "
