"rke2.io/backup_restore\">此页面</link>。<literal>rke2</literal> 二进制文件的"
"默认位置为 <literal>/opt/rke2/bin</literal>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1221
msgid ""
"You can upgrade the RKE2 version using the RKE2 installation script as "
"follows:"
