#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1366
msgid "System upgrade controller deployment guide"
msgstr "系统升级控制器部署指南"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1367
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"strong\">system-upgrade-controller (SUC)</emphasis> is "
"responsible for deploying resources on specific nodes of a cluster based on "
"configurations defined in a custom resource called a <emphasis role=\"strong"
"\">Plan</emphasis>. For more information, see the <link xl:href=\"https://"
"github.com/rancher/system-upgrade-controller\">upstream</link> documentation."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">系统升级控制器 (SUC)</emphasis> 负责根据自定义资源"
"（称为<emphasis role=\"strong\">计划</emphasis>）中定义的配置在指定节点上部署"
"资源。有关详细信息，请参见<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/rancher/system-"
"upgrade-controller\">上游文档</link>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1368
msgid ""
"This section focuses solely on deploying the <literal>system-upgrade-"
"controller</literal>. <emphasis role=\"strong\">Plan</emphasis> resources "
"should be deployed from the following documentations:"
msgstr ""
"本节只会重点介绍如何部署<literal>系统升级控制器</literal>。应根据以下文档部署"
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">计划</emphasis>资源："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1373
msgid ""
"This section assumes that you are going to use Fleet (<xref linkend="
"\"components-fleet\"/>) to orchestrate the <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC</"
"emphasis> deployment. Users using a third-party GitOps workflow should see "
"<xref linkend=\"day2-suc-third-party-gitops\"/> for information on what "
"resources they need to setup in their workflow."
msgstr ""
"本节假设您要使用 Fleet（<xref linkend=\"components-fleet\"/>）来编排 "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC</emphasis> 部署。使用第三方 GitOps 工作流程的用"
"户应参见<xref linkend=\"day2-suc-third-party-gitops\"/>来了解需要在其工作流程"
"中设置哪些资源。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1374
msgid ""
"To determine the resource to use, refer to <xref linkend=\"day2-determine-"
"use-case\"/>."
msgstr ""
"要确定所要使用的资源，请参见<xref linkend=\"day2-determine-use-case\"/>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1375
msgid "SUC deployment using a GitRepo resource"
msgstr "使用 GitRepo 资源进行 SUC 部署"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1376
msgid ""
"This section covers how to create a <literal>GitRepo</literal> resource that "
"will ship the needed <literal>SUC Plans</literal> for a successful <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">SUC</emphasis> deployment to your <emphasis role=\"strong"
"\">target</emphasis> downstream clusters."
msgstr ""
"本节介绍如何创建 <literal>GitRepo</literal> 资源，用于将成功完成 <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">SUC</emphasis> 部署所需的 <literal>SUC 计划</literal>传送到"
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">目标</emphasis>下游群集。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1377
msgid ""
"The Edge team maintains a ready to use <literal>GitRepo</literal> resource "
"for <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC</emphasis> in each of our <literal>suse-"
"edge/fleet-examples</literal> <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/"
"fleet-examples/releases\">releases</link> under <literal>gitrepos/day2/"
"system-upgrade-controller-gitrepo.yaml</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Edge 团队会在每个 <literal>suse-edge/fleet-examples</literal> <link xl:href="
"\"https://github.com/suse-edge/fleet-examples/releases\">版本</link>中的 "
"<literal>gitrepos/day2/system-upgrade-controller-gitrepo.yaml</literal> 下，"
"为 <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC</emphasis> 维护一个随时可用的 "
"<literal>GitRepo</literal> 资源。"

