"If using the <literal>suse-edge/fleet-examples</literal> repository, make "
"sure you are using the resources from a dedicated <link xl:href=\"https://"
"github.com/suse-edge/fleet-examples/releases\">release</link> tag."
msgstr ""
"如果您使用 <literal>suse-edge/fleet-examples</literal> 储存库，请确保使用带有"
"专用<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/fleet-examples/releases\">版"
"本</link>标记的资源。"

