#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1492
msgid ""
"This section assumes you will be deploying the <literal>OS package update</"
"literal> <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC Plan</emphasis> using Fleet (<xref "
"linkend=\"components-fleet\"/>). If you intend to deploy the <emphasis role="
"\"strong\">SUC Plan</emphasis> using a different approach, refer to <xref "
"linkend=\"os-pkg-suc-plan-deployment-third-party\"/>."
msgstr ""
"本节假设您将使用 Fleet（<xref linkend=\"components-fleet\"/>）部署<literal>操"
"作系统软件包更新</literal> <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC 计划</emphasis>。如"
"果您打算使用其他方法部署 <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC 计划</emphasis>，请参"
"见<xref linkend=\"os-pkg-suc-plan-deployment-third-party\"/>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1493
msgid ""
"The <literal>OS package update procedure</literal> revolves around deploying "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC Plans</emphasis> to downstream clusters. These "
"plans then hold information about how and on which nodes to deploy the "
"<literal>edge-update.service</literal> systemd.service. For information "
"regarding the structure of a <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC Plan</emphasis>, "
"refer to the <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/rancher/system-upgrade-"
"controller?tab=readme-ov-file#example-plans\">upstream</link> documentation."
msgstr ""
"<literal>操作系统软件包更新过程</literal>主要围绕着将 <emphasis role=\"strong"
"\">SUC 计划</emphasis>部署到下游群集来进行。然后，这些计划将包含有关如何以及"
"在哪些节点上部署 <literal>edge-update.service</literal> systemd.service 的信"
"息。有关 <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC 计划</emphasis>结构的信息，请参见"
"<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/rancher/system-upgrade-controller?"
"tab=readme-ov-file#example-plans\">上游文档</link>。"

