#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1612
msgid ""
"The <literal>Kubernetes version upgrade procedure</literal> revolves around "
"deploying <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC Plans</emphasis> to downstream "
"clusters. These plans hold information that instructs the <emphasis role="
"\"strong\">SUC</emphasis> on which nodes to create Pods which run the "
"<literal>rke2/k3s-upgrade</literal> images. For information regarding the "
"structure of a <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC Plan</emphasis>, refer to the "
"<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/rancher/system-upgrade-controller?"
"tab=readme-ov-file#example-plans\">upstream</link> documentation."
msgstr ""
"<literal>Kubernetes 版本升级过程</literal>主要围绕着将 <emphasis role="
"\"strong\">SUC 计划</emphasis>部署到下游群集来进行。这些计划包含的信息会告知 "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC</emphasis> 要在哪些节点上创建运行 "
"<literal>rke2/k3s-upgrade</literal> 映像的 Pod。有关 <emphasis role=\"strong"
"\">SUC 计划</emphasis>结构的信息，请参见<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/"
"rancher/system-upgrade-controller?tab=readme-ov-file#example-plans\">上游文档"
