"upgrade on cluster <emphasis role=\"strong\"><emphasis>agent</emphasis></"
"emphasis> nodes. Will <emphasis role=\"strong\">not</emphasis> be "
"interpreted if the cluster consists only from <emphasis>control-plane</"
"emphasis> nodes."
