"由<emphasis>控制平面</emphasis>节点组成，则<emphasis role=\"strong\">不</"
"emphasis>做解释。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1633
msgid ""
"<literal>rke2-plan-control-plane</literal>/<literal>k3s-plan-control-plane</"
"literal> - instructs <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC</emphasis> on how to do a "
"Kubernetes upgrade on cluster <emphasis role=\"strong\"><emphasis>control-"
