#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1636
msgid ""
"Depending on which <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC Plans</emphasis> you have "
"deployed, the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Update Pod</emphasis> will run "
"either a <link xl:href=\"https://hub.docker.com/r/rancher/rke2-upgrade/tags"
"\">rke2-upgrade</link> or a <link xl:href=\"https://hub.docker.com/r/rancher/"
"k3s-upgrade/tags\">k3s-upgrade</link> image and will execute the following "
"workflow on <emphasis role=\"strong\">each</emphasis> cluster node:"
msgstr ""
"根据您部署的 <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC 计划</emphasis>，<emphasis role="
"\"strong\">更新 Pod</emphasis> 将运行 <link xl:href=\"https://hub.docker.com/"
"r/rancher/rke2-upgrade/tags\">rke2-upgrade</link> 或 <link xl:href=\"https://"
"hub.docker.com/r/rancher/k3s-upgrade/tags\">k3s-upgrade</link> 映像，并在"
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">每个</emphasis>群集节点上执行以下工作流程："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1637
msgid ""
"<link xl:href=\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/kubectl/generated/"
