#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1834
msgid ""
"Configure the <literal>eib-chart-upgrade-user-data.yaml</literal> secret "
"located under the <literal>eib-chart-upgrade</literal> fleet that you copied "
"from step (2):"
msgstr ""
"配置您在步骤 2 中复制的 <literal>eib-chart-upgrade</literal> Fleet 目录下的 "
"<literal>eib-chart-upgrade-user-data.yaml</literal> 密钥："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1835
msgid ""
"The secret ships a file called <literal>chart_upgrade_data.txt</literal>. "
"This file holds the chart upgrade data that the <literal>upgrade script</"
"literal> will use to know which charts need to be upgraded. The file expects "
"one-line per chart entries in the following format <emphasis role=\"strong\">"
"\"&lt;name&gt;|&lt;version&gt;|&lt;base64_encoded_archive&gt;\"</emphasis>:"
msgstr ""
"该密钥附带一个名为 <literal>chart_upgrade_data.txt</literal> 的文件。此文件包"
"含 chart 升级数据，<literal>升级脚本</literal>将使用这些数据来了解哪些 chart "
"需要升级。该文件要求以每个 chart 项一行的形式指定配置项，其格式如下："
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">“&lt;name&gt;|&lt;version&gt;|&lt;"
"base64_encoded_archive&gt;”</emphasis>："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1836
msgid ""
"<literal>name</literal> - is the name of the helm chart as seen in the "
"<literal>kubernetes.helm.charts.name[]</literal> property of the EIB "
"definition file."
msgstr ""
"<literal>name</literal> - Helm chart 的名称，如 EIB 定义文件的 "
"<literal>kubernetes.helm.charts.name[]</literal> 属性中所示。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1837
msgid ""
"<literal>version</literal> - should hold the new version of the Helm chart. "
"During the upgrade this value will be used to replace the old "
"<literal>version</literal> value of the <literal>HelmChart</literal> "
"manifest."
msgstr ""
"<literal>version</literal> - 应包含 Helm chart 的新版本。在升级期间，此值用于"
"替换 <literal>HelmChart</literal> 清单的旧 <literal>version</literal> 值。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1838
msgid ""
"<literal>base64_encoded_archive</literal> - pass the output of the "
"<literal>base64 -w 0 &lt;chart-archive&gt;.tgz</literal> here. During "
"upgrade this value will be used to replace the old <literal>chartContent</"
"literal> value of the <literal>HelmChart</literal> manifest."
msgstr ""
"<literal>base64_encoded_archive</literal> - 在此处传递 <literal>base64 -w 0 "
"&lt;chart-archive&gt;.tgz</literal> 的输出。在升级期间，此值用于替换 "
"<literal>HelmChart</literal> 清单的旧 <literal>chartContent</literal> 值。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1839
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"strong\">&lt;name&gt;|&lt;version&gt;|&lt;"
"base64_encoded_archive&gt;</emphasis> line should be removed from the file "
"before you start adding your data. It serves as an example of where and how "
"you should configure your chart data."
msgstr ""
"在开始添加数据之前，应从该文件中去除 <emphasis role=\"strong\">&lt;name&gt;|"
"&lt;version&gt;|&lt;base64_encoded_archive&gt;</emphasis> 行。它是一个示例"
"行，用于说明在何处以及如何配置 chart 数据。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1840
msgid ""
"Configure a <literal>GitRepo</literal> resource that will be shipping your "
"chart upgrade <literal>fleet</literal>. For more information on what a "
"<literal>GitRepo</literal> is, see <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/"
"ref-gitrepo\">GitRepo Resource</link>."
msgstr ""
"配置一个 <literal>GitRepo</literal> 资源用于传送 chart 升级 <literal>fleet</"
"literal>。有关 <literal>GitRepo</literal> 的详细信息，请参见 <link xl:href="
"\"https://fleet.rancher.io/ref-gitrepo\">GitRepo 资源</link>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1841
msgid "Configure <literal>GitRepo</literal> through the Rancher UI:"
msgstr "通过 Rancher UI 配置 <literal>GitRepo</literal>："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1844
msgid ""
"Here pass your <emphasis role=\"strong\">repository data</emphasis> and "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">path</emphasis> to your chart <literal>upgrade "
"fleet</literal>"
msgstr ""
"在此处将您的<emphasis role=\"strong\">储存库数据</emphasis>和<emphasis role="
"\"strong\">路径</emphasis>传递给 chart <literal>升级 fleet</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1845
msgid ""
"Select <emphasis role=\"strong\">Next</emphasis> and specify the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">target</emphasis> clusters of which you want to upgrade the "
"configured charts"
msgstr ""
"选择<emphasis role=\"strong\">下一步</emphasis>，并指定您要对其中已配置的 "
"chart 进行升级的<emphasis role=\"strong\">目标</emphasis>群集"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1847
msgid ""
"If <literal>Rancher</literal> is not available on your setup, you can "
"configure a <literal>GitRepo</literal> manually on your <literal>management "
"cluster</literal>:"
msgstr ""
"如果无法对您的设置使用 <literal>Rancher</literal>，可以在<literal>管理群集</"
"literal>上手动配置 <literal>GitRepo</literal>："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1848
msgid "Populate the following template with your data:"
msgstr "在以下模板中填充您的数据："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1849
msgid ""
"For more information on how to setup and deploy a <literal>GitRepo</literal> "
"resource, see <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/ref-gitrepo\">GitRepo "
"Resource</link> and <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/gitrepo-add"
"\">Create a GitRepo Resource</link>."
msgstr ""
"有关如何设置和部署 <literal>GitRepo</literal> 资源的详细信息，请参见 <link "
"xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/ref-gitrepo\">GitRepo 资源</link>和<link "
"xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/gitrepo-add\">创建 GitRepo 资源</link>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1850
msgid ""
"For information on how to match <emphasis role=\"strong\">taget</emphasis> "
"clusters on a more granular level, see <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher."
"io/gitrepo-targets\">Mapping to Downstream Clusters</link>."
msgstr ""
"有关如何在更精细的级别匹配<emphasis role=\"strong\">目标</emphasis>群集的信"
"息，请参见<link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/gitrepo-targets\">映射到下"
"游群集</link>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1851
msgid ""
"Deploy the configured <literal>GitRepo</literal> resource to the "
"<literal>fleet-default</literal> namespace of the <literal>management "
"cluster</literal>."
msgstr ""
"将配置的 <literal>GitRepo</literal> 资源部署到<literal>管理群集</literal>的 "
"<literal>fleet-default</literal> 名称空间。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1852
msgid ""
"Executing this steps should result in a successfully created "
"<literal>GitRepo</literal> resource. It will then be picked up by Fleet and "
"a Bundle will be created. This Bunlde will hold the <emphasis role=\"strong"
"\">raw</emphasis> Kubernetes resources that the <literal>GitRepo</literal> "
"has configured under its fleet directory."
msgstr ""
"执行这些步骤后，应该可以成功创建 <literal>GitRepo</literal> 资源。然后，"
"Fleet 将拾取该资源，并创建捆绑包。此捆绑包将包含 <literal>GitRepo</literal> "
"在其 Fleet 目录下配置的<emphasis role=\"strong\">原始</emphasis> Kubernetes "
"资源。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1853
msgid ""
"Fleet will then deploy all the Kubernetes resources from the Bundle to the "
"specified downstream clusters. One of this resources will be a SUC Plan that "
"will trigger the chart upgrade. For a full list of the resoruces that will "
"be deployed and the workflow of the upgrade process, refer to the overview "
"(<xref linkend=\"day2-helm-upgrade-eib-chart-overview\"/>) section."
msgstr ""
"然后，Fleet 会将捆绑包中的所有 Kubernetes 资源部署到指定的下游群集。其中一个"
"资源是触发 chart 升级的 SUC 计划。有关要部署的资源的完整列表以及升级过程的工"
"作流程，请参见“概述”（<xref linkend=\"day2-helm-upgrade-eib-chart-overview\"/"
">）一节。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1854
msgid ""
"To track the upgrade process itself, refer to the Monitor SUC Plans (<xref "
"linkend=\"monitor-suc-plans\"/>) section."
msgstr ""
"要跟踪升级过程本身，请参见“监控 SUC 计划”（<xref linkend=\"monitor-suc-plans"
"\"/>）一节。"

