"确定我们要从中获取升级逻辑的 Edge <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-"
"edge/fleet-examples/releases\">版本标记</link>。例如，此示例将使用 "
"<literal>release-3.0.1</literal> 版本标记，它支持的 Longhorn 版本为 "
"<literal>1.6.1</literal>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1873
msgid ""
"Clone the <literal>release-3.0.1</literal> release tag and copy the "
"<literal>fleets/day2/system-upgrade-controller-plans/eib-chart-upgrade</"
