"<literal>${BMC_USERNAME}</literal> — 新裸机主机的 <literal>BMC</literal> 用户"
"名。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2520
