"<literal>URL</literal>（例如 <literal>redfish-virtualmedia://192.168.200.75/"
"redfish/v1/Systems/1/</literal>）。要了解有关硬件提供商支持的不同选项的详细信"
"息，请访问<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/metal3-io/baremetal-operator/"
"blob/main/docs/api.md\">此链接</link>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2523
