#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2533 l10n/source/edge.xml:2578
msgid ""
"The <literal>dataTemplate</literal> to be used as a reference to the "
"template."
msgstr "<literal>dataTemplate</literal>，用作对模板的引用。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2534 l10n/source/edge.xml:2579
msgid ""
"The <literal>hostSelector</literal> to be used matching with the label "
