"first bare-metal host."
msgstr "<literal>${BMC_NODE1_PASSWORD}</literal> — 第一个裸机主机的 BMC 口令。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2556
msgid ""
"<literal>${BMC_NODE1_MAC}</literal> — The MAC address of the first bare-"
