"<literal>kubernetes-vip</literal> service to be used by the "
"<literal>MetalLB</literal> to manage the <literal>VIP</literal> address."
msgstr ""
"用于配置 <literal>kubernetes-vip</literal> 服务的 <literal>end-svc.yaml</"
"literal> 文件，<literal>MetalLB</literal> 使用该服务来管理 <literal>VIP</"
"literal> 地址。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2576
msgid ""
"The last block of information contains the Kubernetes version to be used. "
"The <literal>${RKE2_VERSION}</literal> is the version of <literal>RKE2</"
"literal> to be used replacing this value (for example, "
"<literal>v1.28.10+rke2r1</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"最后一个信息块包含要使用的 Kubernetes 版本。<literal>${RKE2_VERSION}</"
"literal> 是要使用的 <literal>RKE2</literal> 版本，请替换此值（例如替换为 "
"<literal>v1.28.9+rke2r1</literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2580
msgid ""
"The <literal>image</literal> to be used as a reference to the image "
"generated using <literal>EIB</literal> on the previous section (<xref "
"linkend=\"eib-edge-image-connected\"/>), and <literal>checksum</literal> and "
"<literal>checksumType</literal> to be used to validate the image."
msgstr ""
"<literal>image</literal>，用作对上一节（<xref linkend=\"eib-edge-image-"
"connected\"/>）中使用 <literal>EIB</literal> 生成的映像的引用；"
"<literal>checksum</literal> 和 <literal>checksumType</literal>，用于验证映"
"像。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2582
msgid ""
"Once the file is created by joining the previous blocks, the following "
"command has to be executed in the management cluster to start provisioning "
"the new three bare-metal hosts:"
msgstr ""
"通过联接上述块创建该文件后，必须在管理群集中执行以下命令开始置备三个新的裸机"
"主机："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2583
msgid "Advanced Network Configuration"
msgstr "高级网络配置"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2584
msgid ""
"The directed network provisioning workflow allows downstream clusters "
"network configurations such as static IPs, bonding, VLAN’s, etc."
msgstr "定向网络置备工作流程允许使用静态 IP、绑定、VLAN 等下游群集网络配置。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2585
msgid ""
"The following sections describe the additional steps required to enable "
"provisioning downstream clusters using advanced network configuration."
msgstr "以下章节将介绍使用高级网络配置置备下游群集所要执行的附加步骤。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2587
msgid ""
"The image generated using <literal>EIB</literal> has to include the network "
"folder and the script following this section (<xref linkend=\"add-network-eib"
"\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"使用 <literal>EIB</literal> 生成的映像必须包含<xref linkend=\"add-network-eib"
"\"/>一节中所述的 network 文件夹和脚本。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2588 l10n/source/edge.xml:2612
msgid "<emphasis role=\"strong\">Configuration</emphasis>"
msgstr "<emphasis role=\"strong\">配置</emphasis>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2589 l10n/source/edge.xml:2613
msgid ""
"Use the following two sections as the base to enroll and provision the hosts:"
msgstr "基于以下两个章节的内容登记和置备主机："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2590 l10n/source/edge.xml:2614
msgid ""
"Downstream cluster provisioning with Directed network provisioning (single-"
"node) (<xref linkend=\"single-node\"/>)"
msgstr ""
"使用定向网络置备来置备下游群集（单节点）（<xref linkend=\"single-node\"/>）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2591 l10n/source/edge.xml:2615
msgid ""
"Downstream cluster provisioning with Directed network provisioning (multi-"
"node) (<xref linkend=\"multi-node\"/>)"
msgstr ""
"使用定向网络置备来置备下游群集（多节点）（<xref linkend=\"multi-node\"/>）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2592
msgid ""
"The changes required to enable the advanced network configuration are the "
"following:"
msgstr "需要做出以下更改才能启用高级网络配置："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2593
msgid ""
"Enrollment step: The following new example file with a secret containing the "
"information about the <literal>networkData</literal> to be used to "
"configure, for example, the static <literal>IPs</literal> and <literal>VLAN</"
"literal> for the downstream cluster"
msgstr ""
"登记步骤：以下新示例文件中的某个密钥包含有关 <literal>networkData</"
"literal>（用于配置下游群集的静态 <literal>IP</literal> 和 <literal>VLAN</"
"literal> 等设置）的信息"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2594
msgid ""
"This file contains the <literal>networkData</literal> in a <literal>nmstate</"
"literal> format to be used to configure the advance network configuration "
"(for example, <literal>static IPs</literal> and <literal>VLAN</literal>) for "
"the downstream cluster.  As you can see, the example shows the configuration "
"to enable the interface with static IPs, as well as the configuration to "
"enable the VLAN using the base interface.  Any other <literal>nmstate</"
"literal> example could be defined to be used to configure the network for "
"the downstream cluster to adapt to the specific requirements, where the "
"following variables have to be replaced with real values:"
msgstr ""
"此文件包含用于配置下游群集的高级网络配置（例如<literal>静态 IP</literal> 和 "
"<literal>VLAN</literal>）的、采用 <literal>nmstate</literal> 格式的 "
"<literal>networkData</literal>。可以看到，该示例显示了启用采用静态 IP 的接口"
"的配置，以及启用采用基础接口的 VLAN 的配置。可以定义任何其他 "
"<literal>nmstate</literal> 示例来配置下游群集的网络以适应特定要求。必须将示例"
"中的以下变量替换为实际值："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2595
msgid ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_INTERFACE}</literal> — The control-plane interface "
"to be used for the edge cluster (for example, <literal>eth0</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_INTERFACE}</literal> — 用于边缘群集的控制平面接口"
"（例如 <literal>eth0</literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2596
msgid ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_IP}</literal> — The IP address to be used as an "
"endpoint for the edge cluster (must match with the kubeapi-server endpoint)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_IP}</literal> — 用作边缘群集端点的 IP 地址（必须与 "
"kubeapi-server 端点匹配）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2597
msgid ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_PREFIX}</literal> — The CIDR to be used for the "
"edge cluster (for example, <literal>24</literal> if you want <literal>/24</"
"literal> or <literal>255.255.255.0</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_PREFIX}</literal> — 用于边缘群集的 CIDR（例如，如果"
"您要使用 <literal>/24</literal> 子网掩码，请指定 <literal>24</literal>；也可"
"以指定 <literal>255.255.255.0</literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2598
msgid ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_GATEWAY}</literal> — The gateway to be used for the "
"edge cluster (for example, <literal>192.168.100.1</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_GATEWAY}</literal> — 用于边缘群集的网关（例如 "
"<literal>192.168.100.1</literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2599
msgid ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_MAC}</literal> — The MAC address to be used for the "
"control-plane interface (for example, <literal>00:0c:29:3e:3e:3e</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_MAC}</literal> — 用于控制平面接口的 MAC 地址（例如 "
"<literal>00:0c:29:3e:3e:3e</literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2600
msgid ""
"<literal>${DNS_SERVER}</literal> — The DNS to be used for the edge cluster "
"(for example, <literal>192.168.100.2</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${DNS_SERVER}</literal> — 用于边缘群集的 DNS（例如 "
"<literal>192.168.100.2</literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2601
msgid ""
"<literal>${VLAN_ID}</literal> — The VLAN ID to be used for the edge cluster "
"(for example, <literal>100</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${VLAN_ID}</literal> — 用于边缘群集的 VLAN ID（例如 <literal>100</"
"literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2602
msgid ""
"Also, the reference to that secret using "
"<literal>preprovisioningNetworkDataName</literal> is needed in the "
"<literal>BaremetalHost</literal> object at the end of the file to be "
"enrolled in the management cluster."
msgstr ""
"另外，需要在该文件末尾的 <literal>BaremetalHost</literal> 对象中，使用 "
"<literal>preprovisioningNetworkDataName</literal> 引用该密钥，以便能够在管理"
"群集中登记。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2603
msgid ""
"If you need to deploy a multi-node cluster, the same process must be done "
"for the other nodes."
msgstr "如果需要部署多节点群集，必须对其他节点执行相同的过程。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2604
msgid ""
"Provision step: The block of information related to the network data has to "
"be removed because the platform includes the network data configuration into "
"the secret <literal>controlplane-0-networkdata</literal>."
msgstr ""
"置备步骤：必须去除与网络数据相关的信息块，因为平台会将网络数据配置包含在 "
"<literal>controlplane-0-networkdata</literal> 密钥中。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2605
msgid ""
"The <literal>Metal3DataTemplate</literal>, <literal>networkData</literal> "
"and <literal>Metal3 IPAM</literal> are currently not supported; only the "
"configuration via static secrets is fully supported."
msgstr ""
"目前不支持 <literal>Metal3DataTemplate</literal>、<literal>networkData</"
"literal> 和 <literal>Metal3 IPAM</literal>；只有通过静态密钥进行的配置才完全"
"受支持。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2606
msgid "Telco features (DPDK, SR-IOV, CPU isolation, huge pages, NUMA, etc.)"
msgstr "电信功能（DPDK、SR-IOV、CPU 隔离、大页、NUMA 等）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2607
msgid ""
"The directed network provisioning workflow allows to automate the Telco "
"features to be used in the downstream clusters to run Telco workloads on top "
"of those servers."
msgstr ""
"定向网络置备工作流程允许将下游群集中使用的电信功能自动化，以便在这些服务器上"
"运行电信工作负载。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2609
msgid ""
"The image generated using <literal>EIB</literal> has to include the specific "
"Telco packages following this section (<xref linkend=\"add-telco-feature-eib"
"\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"使用 <literal>EIB</literal> 生成的映像必须包含<xref linkend=\"add-telco-"
"feature-eib\"/>一节中所述的特定电信软件包。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2610
msgid ""
"The image generated using <literal>EIB</literal>, as described in the "
"previous section (<xref linkend=\"eib-edge-image-connected\"/>), has to be "
"located in the management cluster exactly on the path you configured on this "
"section (<xref linkend=\"metal3-media-server\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"如上一节（<xref linkend=\"eib-edge-image-connected\"/>）所述使用 "
"<literal>EIB</literal> 生成的映像必须位于管理群集上您按照<xref linkend="
"\"metal3-media-server\"/>一节所述配置的确切路径中。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2616
msgid "The Telco features covered in this section are the following:"
msgstr "本节将介绍以下电信功能："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2617
msgid "DPDK and VFs creation"
msgstr "DPDK 和 VF 创建"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2618
msgid "SR-IOV and VFs allocation to be used by the workloads"
msgstr "工作负载使用的 SR-IOV 和 VF 分配"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2619
msgid "CPU isolation and performance tuning"
msgstr "CPU 隔离和性能微调"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2620
msgid "Huge pages configuration"
msgstr "大页配置"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2621
msgid "Kernel parameters tuning"
msgstr "内核参数微调"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2622
msgid ""
"For more information about the Telco features, see <xref linkend=\"atip-"
"features\"/>."
msgstr "有关电信功能的详细信息，请参见<xref linkend=\"atip-features\"/>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2623
msgid ""
"The changes required to enable the Telco features shown above are all inside "
"the <literal>RKE2ControlPlane</literal> block in the provision file "
"<literal>capi-provisioning-example.yaml</literal>. The rest of the "
"information inside the file <literal>capi-provisioning-example.yaml</"
"literal> is the same as the information provided in the provisioning section "
"(<xref linkend=\"single-node-provision\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"启用上述电信功能所要做出的更改都可以在 <literal>capi-provisioning-example."
"yaml</literal> 置备文件的 <literal>RKE2ControlPlane</literal> 块中完成。"
"<literal>capi-provisioning-example.yaml</literal> 文件中的其余信息与置备相关"
"章节（<xref linkend=\"single-node-provision\"/>）中提供的信息相同。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2624
msgid ""
"To make the process clear, the changes required on that block "
"(<literal>RKE2ControlPlane</literal>) to enable the Telco features are the "
"following:"
msgstr ""
"明确地说，为启用电信功能而需要在该块 (<literal>RKE2ControlPlane</literal>) 中"
"所做的更改如下："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2625
msgid ""
"The <literal>preRKE2Commands</literal> to be used to execute the commands "
"before the <literal>RKE2</literal> installation process. In this case, use "
"the <literal>modprobe</literal> command to enable the <literal>vfio-pci</"
"literal> and the <literal>SR-IOV</literal> kernel modules."
msgstr ""
"指定 <literal>preRKE2Commands</literal>，用于在 <literal>RKE2</literal> 安装"
"过程开始之前执行命令。本例使用 <literal>modprobe</literal> 命令启用 "
"<literal>vfio-pci</literal> 和 <literal>SR-IOV</literal> 内核模块。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2626
msgid ""
"The ignition file <literal>/var/lib/rancher/rke2/server/manifests/configmap-"
"sriov-custom-auto.yaml</literal> to be used to define the interfaces, "
"drivers and the number of <literal>VFs</literal> to be created and exposed "
"to the workloads."
msgstr ""
"指定 ignition 文件 <literal>/var/lib/rancher/rke2/server/manifests/configmap-"
"sriov-custom-auto.yaml</literal>，用于定义要创建的并向工作负载公开的接口、驱"
"动程序及 <literal>VF</literal> 数量。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2627
msgid ""
"The values inside the config map <literal>sriov-custom-auto-config</literal> "
"are the only values to be replaced with real values."
msgstr ""
"只有 <literal>sriov-custom-auto-config</literal> 配置映射中的值可以替换为实际"
"值。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2628
msgid ""
"<literal>${RESOURCE_NAME1}</literal> — The resource name to be used for the "
"first <literal>PF</literal> interface (for example, <literal>sriov-resource-"
"du1</literal>). It is added to the prefix <literal>rancher.io</literal> to "
"be used as a label to be used by the workloads (for example, "
"<literal>rancher.io/sriov-resource-du1</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${RESOURCE_NAME1}</literal> — 用于第一个 <literal>PF</literal> 接口"
"的资源名称（例如 <literal>sriov-resource-du1</literal>）。它将添加到前缀 "
"<literal>rancher.io</literal> 的后面，供工作负载用作标签（例如 "
"<literal>rancher.io/sriov-resource-du1</literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2629
msgid ""
"<literal>${SRIOV-NIC-NAME1}</literal> — The name of the first <literal>PF</"
"literal> interface to be used (for example, <literal>eth0</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${SRIOV-NIC-NAME1}</literal> — 要使用的第一个 <literal>PF</literal> "
"接口的名称（例如 <literal>eth0</literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2630
msgid ""
"<literal>${PF_NAME1}</literal> — The name of the first physical function "
"<literal>PF</literal> to be used. Generate more complex filters using this "
"(for example, <literal>eth0#2-5</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${PF_NAME1}</literal> — 要使用的第一个物理功能 <literal>PF</"
"literal> 的名称。可以使用此名称生成更复杂的过滤器（例如 <literal>eth0#2-5</"
"literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2631
msgid ""
"<literal>${DRIVER_NAME1}</literal> — The driver name to be used for the "
"first <literal>VF</literal> interface (for example, <literal>vfio-pci</"
"literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${DRIVER_NAME1}</literal> — 用于第一个 <literal>VF</literal> 接口的"
"驱动程序名称（例如 <literal>vfio-pci</literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2632
msgid ""
"<literal>${NUM_VFS1}</literal> — The number of <literal>VFs</literal> to be "
"created for the first <literal>PF</literal> interface (for example, "
"<literal>8</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${NUM_VFS1}</literal> — 要为第一个 <literal>PF</literal> 接口创建的 "
"<literal>VF</literal> 数量（例如 <literal>8</literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2633
msgid ""
"The <literal>/var/sriov-auto-filler.sh</literal> to be used as a translator "
"between the high-level config map <literal>sriov-custom-auto-config</"
"literal> and the <literal>sriovnetworknodepolicy</literal> which contains "
"the low-level hardware information. This script has been created to abstract "
"the user from the complexity to know in advance the hardware information. No "
"changes are required in this file, but it should be present if we need to "
"enable <literal>sr-iov</literal> and create <literal>VFs</literal>."
msgstr ""
"提供 <literal>/var/sriov-auto-filler.sh</literal>，用作高级配置映射 "
"<literal>sriov-custom-auto-config</literal> 与包含低级硬件信息的 "
"<literal>sriovnetworknodepolicy</literal> 之间的转换器。创建此脚本的目的是让"
"用户免于提前知道复杂的硬件信息。不需要在此文件中进行更改，但如果我们需要启用 "
"<literal>sr-iov</literal> 并创建 <literal>VF</literal>，则应该提供此脚本。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2634
